<span class="inner">
Austrian masterworks led <br>by an Austrian Maestro
</span>
</a>
<div class="panelContents" id="panel03">
<p class="panelTitle panelClose">PMF 2024<br>
<small>July 12 - July 30 Highlights</small></p>
<img src="../../img/2024/bg_panel_03_l.webp" class="bg">
<img src="../../img/2017/bg_panel.png" class="bg spNone">
<div class="main">
<p class="catch">Austrian masterworks led by an Austrian Maestro</p>
<h2 class="mainTitle">PMF Orchestra [Program B]</h2>
<div class="inner">
<p class="mb20">Making his PMF debut as Principal Conductor, world-renowned Austrian maestro Manfred Honeck will lead a program of 2 core pieces of the Viennese repertoire. Viennese soloist Till Fellner will perform Mozart’s exquisitely refined Piano Concerto No. 22 before the PMF Orchestra takes on Mahler’s Symphony No. 5, in which Mahler’s breadth of experience as Director of the Vienna State Opera is fully brought to bear. From its beloved Adagietto movement to dazzling solos to extended thunderous grandeur, a transformative 75-minute journey awaits!</p>
<p class="fsSmall textRight">Text: Masahide Hayashi</p>
</div>
<div class="inner">
<h3 class="title">Date</h3>
<table class="date">
<tr>
<td><a href="https://www.pmf.or.jp/en/schedule/concert/2024-picnic.html" target="_blank">July 27 (Sat)</a></td>
<td class="access">Picnic Concert <br class="pc">(Sapporo Art Park Outdoor Stage)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="https://www.pmf.or.jp/en/schedule/orchestra/2024-gala.html" target="_blank">July 28 (Sun)</a></td>
<td class="access">PMF GALA Concert <br class="pc">(Sapporo Concert Hall <i>Kitara</i>)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="https://www.pmf.or.jp/en/schedule/orchestra/2024-tokyo.html" target="_blank">July 30 (Tue)</a></td>
<td class="access">PMF Orchestra Concert in Tokyo <br class="pc">(Suntory Hall)</td>
</tr>
</table>
</div>
<div class="inner">
<h3 class="title">Artists</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.pmf.or.jp/en/artist/conductor/2024-C02.html" target="_blank">Manfred Honeck, <i>conductor</i></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.pmf.or.jp/en/artist/program_b/2024-A02.html" target="_blank">Till Fellner, <i>piano*</i></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.pmf.or.jp/en/artist/pmfa/2024-pmfa.html" target="_blank">PMF AMERICA <span class="fsSmall">[appearing on July 27 and July 28]</span></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.pmf.or.jp/en/artist/pmfo/2024-pmfo.html" target="_blank">PMF Orchestra</a></p>
</div>
<div class="inner">
<h3 class="title">Program</h3>
<p>Mozart: Piano Concerto No. 22 in E-flat major, K. 482*</p>
<p>Mahler: Symphony No. 5 in c-sharp minor</p>
</div>
