<div class="row">
<div class="col panel04">
<a href="#panel04" class="panelTrg nopscr">
<span class="inner">
An emerging star &<br class="sm"> PMF alumnus leads <br>the Sapporo Symphony Orchestra
</span>
</a>
<div class="panelContents" id="panel04">
<p class="panelTitle panelClose">PMF 2024<br>
<small>July 12 - July 30 Highlights</small></p>
<img src="../../img/2024/bg_panel_04_l.webp" class="bg">
<img src="../../img/2017/bg_panel.png" class="bg spNone">
<div class="main">
<p class="catch">An emerging star & <br class="pc">PMF alumnus leads the Sapporo Symphony Orchestra</p>
<h2 class="mainTitle">PMF Host City Orchestra Concert</h2>
<div class="inner">
<p class="mb20">Though still in his 30s, Hong Kong born Wilson Ng is already making waves across Asia and beyond. A member of the PMF 2015 Conducting Academy, Ng now returns to lead the PMF Host City Orchestra Concert, featuring the Sapporo Symphony Orchestra! Los Angeles Philharmonic Principal Horn and PMF AMERICA faculty member Andrew Bain will appear as soloist in Toshio Hosokawa’s Horn Concerto “Moment of Blossoming,” a work that seems to bend time itself. The program culminates in Tchaikovsky's beloved Symphony No. 6 "Pathétique." Ng's fresh artistry is sure to manifest this masterwork’s endless wonders.</p>
<p class="fsSmall textRight">Text: Masahide Hayashi</p>
</div>
<div class="inner">
<h3 class="title">Date</h3>
<table class="date">
<tr>
<td><a href="https://www.pmf.or.jp/en/schedule/orchestra/2024-sso.html" target="_blank">July 21 (Sun)</a></td>
<td class="access">PMF Host City Orchestra Concert <br class="pc">(Sapporo Concert Hall <i>Kitara</i>)</td>
</tr>
</table>
</div>
<div class="inner">
<h3 class="title">Artists</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.pmf.or.jp/en/artist/conductor/2024-C03.html" target="_blank">Wilson Ng, <i>conductor</i></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.pmf.or.jp/en/artist/pmfo_faculty/pmfa/2024-F23.html" target="_blank">Andrew Bain, <i>horn*</i></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.pmf.or.jp/en/artist/orchestra/sso/2024-sso.html" target="_blank">Sapporo Symphony Orchestra (PMF Host City Orchestra)</a></p>
<p>Members of the PMF Orchestra</p>
</div>
<div class="inner">
<h3 class="title">Program</h3>
<p>Toshio Hosokawa: Horn Concerto "Moment of Blossoming" *</p>
<p>Tchaikovsky: Symphony No. 6 in b minor, Op. 74 "Pathétique"</p>
</div>
